Package: PowerAnalysisTool
Type: Package
Title: Statistical Power Analysis Tool for Study Design
Version: 5.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Development", "Team", email = "dev@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: A Shiny application for statistical power analysis, sample size
    calculation, and minimal detectable effect estimation for various study designs.
    Supports two-proportion tests, survival analysis, matched case-control studies,
    and continuous outcomes.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
